Exploration enrichment pathways with differentially expressed (DE) genes between old versus young

Team Le Grand

02 mai,2022

Pathway explored : REACTOME INHIBITION OF THE PROTEOLYTIC ACTIVITY OF APC C REQUIRED FOR THE ONSET OF ANAPHASE BY MITOTIC SPINDLE CHECKPOINT COMPONENTS

This pathway contain 21 genes.

In these 21 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).

D2_MuSCs D4_MuSCs
2 2
Mad2l1 Bub1b Bub1b Mad2l1
